        "note_md": {
          "en": "For Core Skills stream nomination applications lodged between 1 July 2026 and 30 June 2027, the Department lists a Core Skills Income Threshold of AUD 79,423. The applicable threshold and market salary rate must be checked at filing.",
          "zh-Hans": "对于 2026 年 7 月 1 日至 2027 年 6 月 30 日提交的核心技能类别提名申请，内政部列出的核心技能收入门槛为 79,423 澳元。递交时必须核对适用门槛和市场薪资。"
        }
